text=(:Summary: Pages in PmWiki that have special meaning or are created or updated in a special manner:)%0aThis is a brief summary of the various "special" pages that occur in PmWiki, along with pointers to other pages with more information as appropriate.%0a%0aThese pages are special because%0a* PmWiki itself creates or updates them (eg [[RecentChanges]], [[Site.AllRecentChanges]])%0a* PmWiki includes them in the default template (eg SideBar)%0a* PmWiki includes them in other pages (eg GroupHeader, GroupFooter)%0a* PmWiki uses them to generate other pages (eg XLPage)%0a* PmWiki uses them in validation or processing (eg [[GroupAttributes]]) %0a* PmWiki uses them to generate content in other pages (eg [[Site.InterMap]], [[Site.PageListTemplates]])%0a%0a[[#recentchanges]]%0a!! Core pages%0a!!! [[Recent Changes]], [[Site.AllRecentChanges]]%0aRecent Changes shows changes made recently to pages in the current group.%0aAll Recent Changes shows changes made recently to pages in all groups.%0a-%3c Documented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Wiki Group(#specialpages)]] - [-{PmWiki/WikiGroup$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! GroupHeader, GroupFooter%0aPage content shown above or below the main content of all pages in the group.%0a-%3c Documented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Group Headers]] - [-{PmWiki/GroupHeaders$:Summary}-]%0a* [[PmWiki/Wiki Group(#specialpages)]] - [-{PmWiki/WikiGroup$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Side Bar]], SideBar [--({Site/SideBar$:Summary})--]%0aThis Page is displayed at the left side of the main text. It contains the essential Links to your WikiPages. There is one for the site and may be one for each group. The Links are listed in unnumbered lists. Precede the headers with [@%25sidehead%25@]. In the default SideBar, there is a link to @@edit@@ this page. %0aAt last follow the rules for editing pages.%0a-%3cDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Skins]] - [-{PmWiki/Skins$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Page Actions]] [--({Site/PageActions$:Summary})--]%0aDocumented in%0a(:pagelist fmt=#titlesummary order=name name=PmWiki/AvailableActions,PmWiki/SitePageActions,PmWiki/CustomActions :)%0a[[Security]] in PmWiki is applied through page actions.%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Edit Form]] [--({Site/EditForm$:Summary})--]%0aThis page is displayed for the edit [[AvailableActions|action]].%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Auth Form]] [--({Site/AuthForm$:Summary})--]%0aThis page is displayed when a [[password(s)]] is required to perform the requested [[AvailableActions|action]].%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Page Not Found]] [--({Site/PageNotFound$:Summary})--]%0aThe text shown when a page is not found (usually when a new page is to be created)%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Preferences]] [--({Site/Preferences$:Summary})--]%0aThis page can be used as template for (personal) preferences, or set as default site preference.%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Search]] [--({Site/Search$:Summary})--]%0aThe text shown when someone makes a search using the built-in PmWiki search facilities, i.e. [=(:searchbox:)=].%0a-%3c Documented in%0a%0a* [[PmWiki/Search]] - [-{PmWiki/Search$:Summary}-]%0a* [[PmWiki/Search For Pages]] - [-{PmWiki/SearchForPages$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[Group Attributes]] [--({PmWiki/GroupAttributes$:Summary})--]%0aDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Group Attributes]] - [-{PmWiki/GroupAttributes$:Summary}-]%0a* [[PmWiki/Wiki Group(#specialpages)]] - [-{PmWiki/WikiGroup$:Summary}-]%0a* [[PmWiki/Passwords]] - [-{PmWiki/Passwords$:Summary}-]%0a* [[PmWiki/Security]] - [-{PmWiki/Security$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Page List Templates]], [[Site.Local Templates]] [--({Site/PageListTemplates$:Summary})--]%0aDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/PageLists]] - [-{PmWiki/PageLists$:Summary}-]%0a* [[PmWiki/PageList Templates]] - [-{PmWiki/PageListTemplates$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[SiteAdmin.Auth User]] [--({SiteAdmin/AuthUser$:Summary})--]%0aDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Auth User]] - [-{PmWiki/AuthUser$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[Site/Inter Map]] [--({Site/InterMap$:Summary})--]%0aList external Internet sites shortcuts. %0aSee [[PmWiki/InterMap]] documentation.%0a%0a!!! [[Site/Edit Quick Reference]] [--({Site/EditQuickReference$:Summary})--]%0aContains the 'help' text that appears at the bottom of the edit window (before the preview area)%0a%0a!!! [[Site/Upload Quick Reference]] [--({Site/UploadQuickReference$:Summary})--]%0aContains the 'help' text that appears when uploading a file with [@Attach:file.ext@] at the bottom of the upload window%0a%0a!!! [[SiteAdmin.Approved Urls]] [--({SiteAdmin/ApprovedUrls$:Summary})--]%0aDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Url Approvals]] - [-{PmWiki/UrlApprovals$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! [[SiteAdmin.Blocklist]] [--({SiteAdmin/Blocklist$:Summary})--]%0aSee [[PmWiki/Blocklist]]%0a%0a!!! [[Site.Notify List]] [--({SiteAdmin/NotifyList$:Summary})--]%0aDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Notify]] - [-{PmWiki/Notify$:Summary}-]%0a%0a!!! Recent Uploads%0aSee [[Cookbook:RecentUploadsLog]]%0a%0a!!! XLPage, XLPageLocal%0aDocumented in%0a* [[PmWiki/Internationalizations]] - [-{PmWiki/Internationalizations$:Summary}-]%0a(:pagelist fmt=#XLPagelist Group=PmWiki* list=normal order=$:Language $:Language=- :)%0a>>comment%3c%3c%0a[[#XLPagelist]]%0a(:template first:)%0a->%0a(:template each:)%0a[-[[{=$Group}/XLPage | {=$Group}]] -]%0a[[#XLPagelistend]]%0a>>%3c%3c%0a%0a%0a!!! Group.HomePage Group.Group%0aGroup's default page $DefaultPage%0a* [[PmWiki/Wiki Group(#groupdefaultpage)]] - [-{PmWiki/WikiGroup$:Summary}-]%0a%0a%0a!! wikilib.d%0aThe wikilib.d directory contains the default version of all of the pages required for an operating installation of a PmWiki site.  When you later upgrade from one version of the software to the next, that directory, and all of the files in it, will be replaced with a new set. So it is not recommended that you edit or alter any of the files in that directory yourself.  HOWEVER, when you edit an existing page '''from within the wiki''' (by clicking "edit" while viewing the page, making changes in the edit box, and saving) the software will create a new version of that page, and store it in the directory wiki.d. Whenever there is a page in wiki.d with the same name as one in wikilib.d, the wiki will always serve up the one in wiki.d.  This is how you customize your own site, without having to be concerned about preserving or over-writing the default bundle in wikilib.d.%0a%0a!! Recipe based%0a%0a!!! [[SiteAdmin.Auth List]] [--({SiteAdmin/AuthList$:Summary})--]%0aAn automatically generated list of all groups or pages with individual permissions (attributes, passwords).%0a%0a!!! New page templates%0aDocumented in%0a* [[Cookbook.EditTemplates]] - [-{Cookbook.EditTemplates$:Summary}-]%0a%0a%0a!!! All groups Header and Footer%0aDocumented in%0a* [[Cookbook.AllGroupHeader]] - [-{Cookbook.AllGroupHeader$:Summary}-]
